Lines 297-299: Pipeline triggers reference `src/mnemonic/**` and `migrations/**` paths. The actual migration directory shown in `data-storage.md` is `src/mnemonic/migrations/postgres/`. The trigger pattern should be consistent with the actual directory layout.

