Lines 199-219: The diagram in ADR-004 shows `ROUTE[Routing Engine]` as a subgraph component. While ADR-004 has a note at line 197 saying "Retained for historical context," the diagram could confuse readers skimming the document.

---

### L-6. `00-overview.md` Missing `data-storage.md` in Design Documents Table

The Available Design Documents table (lines 173-182) lists pattern-processing, configuration, observability-implementation, and routing-engine, but omits `data-storage.md` which is one of the most important post-pivot design documents.

